{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"92448-huihua-youxi","title":"绘画游戏","description":"吉努和她的奶奶画了圆形、三角形和正方形， 然后把它们变成各种各样的东西。这个简单的故事向儿童介绍形状的概念，并鼓励他们运用他们的想象力。 这个简单的故事向儿童介绍形状的概念，并鼓励他们运用他们的想象力。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Ajanta Guhathakurta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/92448-huihua-youxi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/716431/size3/6bc9c1887a5230a7f0d6708d14a9982d.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/716431/size6/6bc9c1887a5230a7f0d6708d14a9982d.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61941/size6/74c918967c4d2f91ab82e34fd97b5061.jpg","text":"吉努在她奶奶家过暑假。\n吉努\n说：“奶奶，陪我玩！”\n 她在这里没有朋友，觉得好无聊。\n奶奶说：“去拿一块粉笔，我们来玩个游戏。”","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61942/size6/00b15cb504186654e4ce838a7bca6ae4.jpg","text":"吉努很兴奋。 奶奶会和她玩什么游戏呢？ 奶奶画了一个形状。\n 她问：“猜猜这是什么？”\n \n吉努不高兴地回答：“这是个圆形。” 她不喜欢这个无聊的游戏。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61943/size6/e8d52fcd277537b0ef932f37df27fd89.jpg","text":"奶奶说：“是的，但是圆形也可以变出更多东西。”\n吉努想了一下，然后笑了。\n“这是一个笑脸！”她说道。\n奶奶拍拍手，说：“很好，\n你知道怎么玩这个游戏！”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61944/size6/9fe4ae4bf9e2eae1500e258f219762f7.jpg","text":"“奶奶你看，我画了什么！”吉努说道。\n \n活动：你能用三个圆形画出什么呢？","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61945/size6/b64e6d86412658f0ed66c1dff9c329ec.jpg","text":"奶奶画了另一个形状。\n“是三角形！”吉努喊道。\n然后她笑了。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61947/size6/411e0775820a96a48094351e3150d01c.jpg","text":"“奶奶你看，我画了什么！”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61948/size6/59dc555620afbcfcbb6ecbd54cdcbcc1.jpg","text":"“吉努，做得好！”奶奶说道。 “你看，谁来和我们一起玩了？”\n \n活动：你可以用三个圆形和四个三角形画出什么？","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61949/size6/087110cf512d05049e9131e3176742e9.jpg","text":"奶奶画了有四个边的形状。 \n“这是一个长方形吗？”吉努问道。\n奶奶回答：“你仔细看， 所有的边都一样长。\n” \n“这是一个正方形！ 嗯......奶奶你看，我画了个窗口。\n”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61950/size6/4a51c91d31a9974cf09599af038c274d.jpg","text":"“你要在窗口旁边画一棵树吗？”奶奶问她。\n“是的奶奶，谢谢你！”吉努说。\n 她看着所有的粉笔画。 她现在可以上色了吗？\n活动：你可以用一个三角形和一个长方形画出什么？","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61951/size6/c70545dbe6c0695820e27657efa33705.jpg","text":"不久，吉努举起了她的画。 \n“哇，好多圆形、三角形和正方形！“奶奶说道。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61952/size6/1d12c5339f010a03d26cba082b5c29d1.jpg","text":"“嗯，奶奶，不止这样！ 这里有一只鸟，正在飞回树上的家。 还有你猜，谁来一起吃午饭？","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/61953/size6/6d95c5d22a642c211633f36124b484b6.jpg","text":"奶奶称赞她：“吉努，你好聪明啊！” \n吉努还想要画更多。 她和奶奶接下来会画什么呢？\n活动：你可以用圆形、三角形和正方形画出什么？","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":47}}